headline: These 3 Stocks Have Done Something Only 33% of the S&P 500 Has Managed So Far in 2025
summary: Obviously, it's been a tough start to the year for the stock market.  As of this writing, the S&P 500, Nasdaq Composite, and Dow Jones Industrial Average are down 10%, 16%, and 7%, respectively, year to date.  Jake Lerch (Palantir Technologies): My choice is Palantir Technologies (NASDAQ: PLTR).
